        "min": 10,
        "max": 90,
        "value": 70,
        "unit": "%",
        "description": "Ensures uniform coverage on porous terracotta; 70% optimal to avoid gaps or uneven heating. Source: Process optimization in laser scanning studies (e.g., Salonitis et al., 2013, Opt. Lasers Eng.)."
